{"tid":2267527,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紐約港人集會聲援「維尼」控訴北京惡行","createTime":"2020-11-02T06:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T08:35:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1f7ec36fcfbfb5edd12aad3b617631960d9d7d0a","tid":2267527,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T06:40:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/OOOD6WDFC5AJ7ETC4WIVTGTZSY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2FOOOD6WDFC5AJ7ETC4WIVTGTZSY%2F&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxQi%2F3qgDO6vJfpFVPRJtUZY%3D&h=e0312a9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2FOOOD6WDFC5AJ7ETC4WIVTGTZSY%2F&h=864b5dea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/OOOD6WDFC5AJ7ETC4WIVTGTZSY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n紐約港人集會聲援「維尼」控訴北京惡行<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中共近年加強打壓香港，新疆、西藏等少數民族亦同樣遭受迫害。美國港人組織「Project Black Mask HK」於萬聖節，.....................................................，指不少港人已被噤聲，自己更應無懼站出來，「唔應該每次都躲在鍵盤後畀like」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AD4XsfTtIwcqduR4s_gzzK-auGk=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FNKU4YYGEVF3DHZGCNAOPME7JY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAD4XsfTtIwcqduR4s_gzzK-auGk%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFNKU4YYGEVF3DHZGCNAOPME7JY.jpg&h=684edc6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■紐約港人日前裝扮成小熊維尼舉行集會，聲援所有受中共壓迫的民族。何家達攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冀團結遭迫害民族<br />\n<br />\n集會今年已第二次舉行，受疫情影響改在華盛頓廣場公園舉辦，10多人打扮成「小熊維尼」，吸引約40多人圍觀，包括不少當地人。參加者高舉「光復香港、時代革命」、「願榮光歸香港」等旗幟，高叫「Stand with Hong Kong」等口號，各少數民族代表逐一講述中共對他們的迫害。<br />\n<br />\n發起活動的「Project Black Mask HK」負責人Joyce稱，希望透過集會讓所有被中共壓迫的民族團結一起，讓更多美國人知道中國對他們的威脅，「如果唔走在一起，好難打贏呢場仗」。<br />\n<br />\n在美國出生、父母是香港人的Joyce坦言，香港實施港版國安法後，她未有太大憂慮，因為她不打算回港。「我就希望用呢種權利去幫其他人，包括香港人，香港人嘅小朋友（抗爭者），好唔好彩有呢個大陸政府。」<br />\n<br />\n今年她首次可投票選美國總統，她認為現任總統特朗普任內幫了香港不少，包括通過不少法案，「𠵱家睇拜登似冇咁幫到手，自己都有啲掙扎」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VQyBBHxLLyY1WdlAcZCzhOhm20w=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LN5BOTQ4A5GHFDPJJGGMN2ULBE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVQyBBHxLLyY1WdlAcZCzhOhm20w%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLN5BOTQ4A5GHFDPJJGGMN2ULBE.jpg&h=0b563400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■參加者盼令美國人了解中共惡行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fC5JNaim_86FpVxvazkI1lJ-itI=/356x522/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZGI3ULA2WRCV7FP66RLV563O7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfC5JNaim_86FpVxvazkI1lJ-itI%3D%2F356x522%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZGI3ULA2WRCV7FP66RLV563O7Y.jpg&h=ae6f3be9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「應該躲鍵盤後面」<br />\n<br />\n另一參與者Winnie（化名）稱，集會有助更多美國人了解中共，他更希望告訴香港人，「我哋（紐約港人）係支持佢哋」。<br />\n<br />\n香港實施港版國安法後，他坦言有所顧慮，擔心從此無法回港，「走出來都要好大勇氣，但又咁諗，好多香港朋友已經屈住講唔出來，如果我唔講，唔通只係等全世界最出名嗰幾位去發聲講？每人都應發聲，唔應該每次都躲在鍵盤後面畀like」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鍾雅宜、何家達、林偉誠美國直擊<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dldhdScatWJ760InV2JPEQ5n-uk=/1772x1181/filters:quality\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdldhdScatWJ760InV2JPEQ5n-uk%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxQi%2F3qgDO6vJfpFVPRJtUZY%3D&h=ebb5103e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdldhdScatWJ760InV2JPEQ5n-uk%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality&h=48f69ae1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dldhdScatWJ760InV2JPEQ5n-uk=/1772x1181/filters:quality</a>(100)/<a href=\"http://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Z7CDGZDVKZDKXIDPHWETGMW7WI.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZ7CDGZDVKZDKXIDPHWETGMW7WI.jpg&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxQi%2F3qgDO6vJfpFVPRJtUZY%3D&h=7f9a3464\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Z7CDGZDVKZDKXIDPHWETGMW7WI.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"54fbb1c6c6f3fe14dd05b47d4082387953e99c70","tid":2267527,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:13:44.000Z","msg":"Good and Thanks"},{"pid":"725598af13ba46666b0c02a534bdb1e9b69e4bf8","tid":2267527,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:19:42.000Z","msg":"Winnie<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78f9cd07bf84c4440a6d130da5a16a8d4e3babe","tid":2267527,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}